[19/07/2018 19:30:58] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola.</font>
[19/07/2018 19:31:02] <font color="#ffffff">¿El quebequés?</font>
[19/07/2018 19:31:02] <font color="#ffffff">Eso es.</font>
[19/07/2018 19:31:05] <font color="#ffffff">La anfitriona nos da permiso</font>
